{"tid":826694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵奇人】奇男東涌綫車廂玩雜耍 女伴全程拍攝惹反感","createTime":"2018-09-18T11:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T11:59:17.000Z","uid":202698,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a57bc593dc6f5e1d1bb4ca7cb68b20ca47cc521b","tid":826694,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180918/1/67/1/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%A5%87%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A5%87%E7%94%B7%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E7%B6%AB%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E7%8E%A9%E9%9B%9C%E8%80%8D-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E6%83%B9%E5%8F%8D%E6%84%9F-9244534.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F1%2F67%2F1%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25A5%2587%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25A5%2587%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E7%258E%25A9%25E9%259B%259C%25E8%2580%258D-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%25E6%2583%25B9%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2584%259F-9244534.html&d=qu2zEATov2gwXhtY4ibB6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ada66da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180918/1/67/1/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%A5%87%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A5%87%E7%94%B7%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E7%B6%AB%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E7%8E%A9%E9%9B%9C%E8%80%8D-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E6%83%B9%E5%8F%8D%E6%84%9F-9244534.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/09/18/2/2ee33b5ac9fcb14530035264a5fe69da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F2%2F2ee33b5ac9fcb14530035264a5fe69da.jpg&h=30401261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GZxcuH_sjFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGZxcuH_sjFw&d=qu2zEATov2gwXhtY4ibB6Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c801ff8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GZxcuH_sjFw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不知為何，港鐵車廂總會吸引一些奇人異士，成為他們表演的舞台，<span style=\"color: red;\">最近又有奇男在東涌綫車廂玩雜耍，除了利用車廂內的橫柱做引體上升外，更對著車窗玻璃打拳，過程中一名女伴一直在旁拍攝，令人嘖嘖稱奇。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨晚有網民於 Facebook 群組「香港突發事故報料區」分享一段影片，晚上 7 時許，一名輛由東涌站開出往香港列車上，一名長髮男子在車廂內進行「表演」，從影片可見，當時車廂乘客數目不算太多，長髮男子先利用橫柱做引體上升，然後轉換倒吊姿勢，落地後又面向車窗玻璃，望著倒影打拳，更令人覺得奇怪的是，長髮男子進行表演時，<span style=\"color: red;\">身旁一名同行的女子一直舉機拍攝，令人好奇二人的關係。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發帖者補充指列車抵達南昌站時，長髮男繼續其表演。<br />\n<br />\n有眼利的網民認出片中男子是沉寂一時，<span style=\"color: red;\">曾經於網絡熱爆的「龍心」，有人笑言「山竹」將他吹醒。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/09/18/8/8bae322e183494d1023b3807ebe15d57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F8%2F8bae322e183494d1023b3807ebe15d57.jpg&h=f44d84fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">亦有網民批評他的行為滋擾欠缺公德，也有網民認為同行的女性同樣惹人反感。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/09/18/d/d8bf25255a356b76c6859a079deb23f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2Fd%2Fd8bf25255a356b76c6859a079deb23f1.jpg&h=1ded8dbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06eabc3149692f9abebc79de1520f62c63c38297","tid":826694,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:50:27.000Z","msg":"阿卡沙!"},{"pid":"ad27f739a365877fc48149213b76dbecb309f154","tid":826694,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"Bobo boy"},{"pid":"aa44a47e876060da293f1bb13a6f5c5ba2ca1394","tid":826694,"uid":154759,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"Do u understand?"},{"pid":"9f2ff46e4eb9027dbec09e1cd2227c559fca2a95","tid":826694,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:56:31.000Z","msg":"天道揼7你"},{"pid":"e1fb0f3e0b7a374a9e118963a41f6f3e082512f1","tid":826694,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"劉馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}